<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/TRACTION CONTROL: BENDIX - TROUBLESHOOTING - 2000, 4000 &#38; 8000 MODELS - TROUBLESHOOTING
        - INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART B
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART B</title>
        <para>Perform
            <hotlnk document="s04033_9.xml" xrefid="t0403303">INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART A, before performing
                this test!
            </hotlnk>
        </para>
        <table id="t0403304" tblwidth="full-page" frame="all" numbered="no" view="reveal">
            <title>Inspection For Illuminated LEDs, Part B</title>
            <tgroup cols="5" colsep="1" rowsep="1" align="center" charoff="50">
                <colspec colname="1" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="0.74in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="0.78in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="1.65in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="1.80in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="1.71in"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="5" spanname="1to5"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>STEP</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>KEY</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>ACTION</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>YES / IN SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>NO / OUT OF SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody valign="top">
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Note if RED ECU LED is illuminated.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_11.xml" xrefid="t0403305">TESTING FOR POWER TO THE CONTROLLER
                                </hotlnk>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>There should be a minimum of three RED LEDS illuminated. Of the three there must be
                                one from each of the following: 1. FRT or RER 2. RHT or LFT 3. MOD or SEN. Are there 3
                                LEDs illuminated?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Replace the controller, then rerun
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_7.xml" xrefid="t0403301">INITIAL START-UP TEST
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Note if the MOD LED is illuminated. Is MOD LED illuminated?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Using the two positioning LEDs (RHT/LFT and FRT/RER), go to the appropriate table
                                starting with
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_12.xml" xrefid="t0403306">TESTING THE LEFT FRONT MODULATOR,
                                    PART A</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Note if the SEN LED is illuminated. Is SEN LED illuminated?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Using the two positioning LEDs (RHT/LFT and FRT/RER), go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_20.xml" xrefid="t0403314">TESTING WHEEL SPEED SENSORS</hotlnk>,
                                and test the appropriate wheel sensor.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>System tests good.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </svcproc>
